            <h2 class=3D"city_description_title">About Brampton </h2>
            <div id=3D"city_description_text">
                <div id=3D"city_desc_txt">Brampton, a city in the Greater T=
oronto Area, is one of Canada's fastest growing cities. Also known as Canad=
a's Flower City, Brampton boasts thousands of acres of parkland and a varie=
ty of outdoor activities. <br><br>

As one of Canada's largest cities, Brampton has a strong economic base, off=
ering residents various hospitals, libraries, places of worship, and school=
s. According to the Province of Ontario, Brampton is a designated urban gro=
wth area. Combined with the beautiful parks, strong economy, and safety, Br=
ampton residents experience a high quality of life. <br><br>

Let's face it - living in the Greater Toronto Area is more affordable than =
living in Toronto. If you work in public transportation is easily accessibl=
e between Toronto and Brampton. As one of the youngest communities in the T=
oronto area, Brampton is a great place to begin your search for a family fr=
iendly home. <br></div>
